snippet.title: Get READY TO CRY FROM LAUGHING too hard! - Best FUNNY DOG VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Dogs are the best and the funniest pets. They never fail to make us laugh extremely hard! This funny dog compilation is ultra hard try not to laugh challenge ever! Look how all these dogs and puppies, fail, make funny sounds, play, sleep, get angry,... So super funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
